    <category term="Claude" scheme="http://example.com/tags/Claude/"/>
    <content>
      <![CDATA[<p>Win+R输入cmd启动命令行：</p><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">npm install -g @anthropic-ai&#x2F;claude-code<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><p>验证版本，成功会显示版本号：</p><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">claude --version<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><p>输入：</p><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">claude<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><p>一般会有错误：</p><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">Unable to connect to Anthropic services    Failed to connect to api.anthropic.com: ERR_BAD_REQUEST    Note: Claude Code might not be available in your country.<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><p>没挂全局代理导致的。</p><p>解决方法参考：<br><a href="https://gist.github.com/docularxu/db0053008b9f41328f29d39ffcf7c2b2?permalink_comment_id=6014130">https://gist.github.com/docularxu/db0053008b9f41328f29d39ffcf7c2b2?permalink_comment_id=6014130</a></p><p><a href="https://www.cnblogs.com/wzzkaifa/p/19079594">https://www.cnblogs.com/wzzkaifa/p/19079594</a></p><p>用Clash Verge，检查端口设置，我的是7897，然后在命令行：</p><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">set http_proxy&#x3D;http:&#x2F;&#x2F;127.0.0.1:7897<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><p>现在可以进入Claude了，会显示：</p><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">Welcome to Claude Code v2.1.89    Let&#39;s get started.<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><p><img src="/images/claude.png" alt="claude界面"></p><p>先让你选择theme，然后就会启动浏览器让你登录Claude账号，进入Claude console。<br>这里应该是让你认证账户。</p><p>我选择获取deepseekAPI，用下面的平台登录，在API keys里创建就好了：<br><a href="https://platform.deepseek.com/">https://platform.deepseek.com</a></p><p>需要永久配置的话，在系统变量里新建变量：<br>ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL&#x3D;<a href="https://api.deepseek.com/anthropic">https://api.deepseek.com/anthropic</a><br>ANTHROPIC_AUTH_TOKEN&#x3D;”自己的API密钥”<br>ANTHROPIC_MODEL&#x3D;deepseek-chat<br>ANTHROPIC_SMALL_FAST_MODEL&#x3D;deepseek-chat</p>]]>
    </content>
